Dialogs.Dialog: Manaka
▲主人公＊▲.
Hehe.
Don't stare at me too much. I'm embarrassed...
L-a-t-e-r▼ Okay？
Why are you wearing a wedding dress, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...？
It's my only chance to wear one... Does it suit me？
Yeah, very much. No, that's not the point...
Hehe, you look so handsome in your tuxedo, you know？
Well, thank you... Tuxedo！？ Me？
Stop that already. Get a grip on yourself, my husband.
Er... Then this is... Is this a wedding for us, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！？
I may be inexperienced, but please take care of me for many years to come.
Yes, same here...
That won't do. You have to properly say the vow.
Vow？ Er... What was I supposed to say？
"Zettai uwaki wa shimasen." (I definitely won't cheat.)
...Well, of course I won't cheat！
You also won't work too much overtime and will be home every day for dinner？
Okay, okay！
That's right. Speaking of our home, I'd like to live in a house with a garden.
A house, huh？ Well, I'll do my best...
Yeah. As for kids... I want enough to make a whole baseball team.
9 of them！？
It's 10 if you include a reserve player. After that...
W-Wait a second. I seem to have lost my confidence...
Geez.
I am ashamed...
Then I'll put up with it all if you just promise me one thing.
All right. Just one thing？ Bring it on！
To forever love and cherish me. In sickness and in health, till death do us part.
Will you swear？
...I do.
I'm so happy...
Say... After this, do you know what you have to do？
Yeah. The kiss to affirm the oath...
You can't！
Eh！？ But we're supposed to！
It's against school rules.
Even that is in the school rules！？
Come on, the bell is ringing. You'll be late for class.
Bell？ Is this sound possibly...
A dream？ Well, of course...
I see. You will marry someone... someday ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
(Speaking of weddings, it's a vow kiss...)
(The wedding dress looks great...)
(“No way, I will not cheat”...)

Sea bathing in hot weather like this is really nice.
But there are couples everywhere. It feels so lonely to be alone.
Manaka
...Hey. I said hey.
Eh？
Hey, why are you looking around restlessly like that？ We finally came to the ocean together...
▲高嶺＊＊▲！ T-That outfit！？
We are at the ocean. Isn't it normal to wear a swimsuit？
Right. I think you're right...
Come on. Are you getting dizzy from the heat？ Hey. Can you put this sunscreen on for me？
Sunscreen？
Yes, please.
You want me to smear it on you！？
You don't want to？ Then maybe I should ask other guys...
Ah！！ Stop！ I'll do it！
Haha, I was just kidding. How could I ask anyone other than you to do this？ ...Then, please do.
O-Okay...
Hey, put it on my back.
No, don't just touch it. You need to rub it all over my back.
It's cold... Ah, this feels good...
Hmm... How is it...？
Hehe. You are good at this. ...Keep going like this...
...Yeah. Right. Just like that. Ah！ It's ticklish...
(W-Why am I getting so nervous...？)
But this really feels good...
...Are you used to doing this？
No way！ How could that be！？
Hmm... Should I believe you？ Just kidding.
This really feels good... I'm going to fall asleep...
That's okay. I'll look out for you.
...No. I don't know if you put the sunscreen on my back properly or not.
Hm？ Then shall I apply some more sunscreen for you？
...What if you pretended to apply the sunscreen but actually did something else while I was sleeping？
I'd never do something like that！
Really？ I feel like your voice is trembling though.
That's because you said something weird all of a sudden, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
W-What's that sound！？
As I thought...
Huh！？
Did you forget？ Whenever you lie, the alarm will go off and you will be arrested. It's a law.
What！？
See？ The police is coming this way.
This can't be true...！
Hah！！
A dream...？ Phew. Thank goodness.
Urgh. Somehow, I have a sore arm...
(Back... Is it really fine？)
(She want me to put suntan oil on her back ...)
(Alright, let's apply sun oil to the back...)

(Where is this place？ It's so bright...)
(Ah, a rabbit. Maybe I should just follow it...)
Manaka
Welcome to the Land of Rabbits.
Waah！！ Ah...！ Why do you look like that ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Why...？ I'm a rabbit. I always look like this.
Eh？
This is the land of lonely rabbits... I invited you here.
Say, did you know？ Rabbits can die of loneliness！
That's a superstition...
No！ I can't stand the loneliness when the person I love is not near me. I can't be away from the one I love.
...Is it okay for you when I'm not around？
That's completely not true！
That's great. Then you will live with me, right？ At this Land of Rabbits.
Yes, of course.
I'm happy！ Before you change your mind, you'd better do the welcoming ritual. Do your best for me！
Welcoming ritual？
Yes. First, place your palms on your head and pretend they are rabbit ears.
L-Like this...？
Yes. Next, swear, "I am a resident of the Land of Rabbits now！" and jump around me 3 times.
What！？
Of course, you have to jump like a rabbit, okay？
(I have to say, "Boku wa usagi no kuni no kokumin ni naru pyon！")
Boku wa usagi no kuni no kokumin ni naru pyon！ (I am a resident of the Land of Rabbits now！) Urgh...
What is it？ Are you tired already？
I'm more embarrassed than tired... Do I really have to do this？
Hmm... So you intend to leave me with this lonely feeling...
I-I'll do it！ I am a resident of the Land of Rabbits now！ Yeah！ Yeah！
I'm so happy. You're one of us now. Then here. Take this.
This is a... carrot？
Yes. Freshly harvested carrot. It's for our celebration, so go ahead.
...R-Raw carrot？
Right. Raw carrots taste the best. So, go ahead.
Um... At least give me some mayonnaise or dressing...
You are not going to eat my carrot...？ Now you're making me feel lonely again...
I'll eat it！
(Urgh... To eat the whole raw carrot... This is so painful...)
How is it？ It was prepared specially for you. It's a pesticide-free, chemical- free, organic carrot▼
Y-Yeah... But can I have some water to drink now？
What are you saying？ Rabbits don't drink water, you know？
Wait！ That's wrong information！ You have to feed rabbits water too！
...Well, you are getting used to living in my land now, right？
(She's ignoring me...)
You will never make me feel lonely ever again, right？
I will never make you feel lonely ever again, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Eh？ A dream...？
Right. I should be with her more often... ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
(“I will be a citizen of the rabbit country！”...)

...Eh？ This is... the hospital？ Am I sick or something？
Manaka
How do you feel？
Ah. Hmm... Why are you dressed like that, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
I am Nightingale.
Hah！？ Nightingale...？ Is this a stage play or something？
What...？ Ah, you must be confused, right？
(Hmm, she's so into her role.)
May I measure your temperature？ Please excuse me...
W-What！？
I'll use my forehead to check your forehead's temperature now.
A-Ah, really...？
(Her face is getting so close. Whoa. I'm really nervous now, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
(...Ah, your hair is getting in my nose ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
...You seem to be fine. How do you feel？
No, I'm going to sneeze... A-Ac...
What's the matter？
(I'm going to sneeze...)
Are you okay？
(I can't hold it. I really have to sneeze...)
Achoo！
Kyaa...
Sorry！ I couldn't hold it in, and...
...No, please don't worry about that. Moreover...
Can I stay with you for a little longer？
Eh？ Oh, of course！
Thank you very much. I apologize for troubling you.
(Urgh... Now that she's so close and staring at me like that...)
...I'm such a bad nurse. For me to feel like this...
Eh？
But I really can't hold it now. I really can't hold back...
Ah, first of all, can you light the candle for me？
Right. We can't see each other's face if it's dark！
Please light the candle for me. I beg you.
Candle, right...？
Great... I'm not very good with darkness.
I'm sorry to show my embarrassing side to a patient like you. Teehee！
Teehee？ You acted like that because you were just afraid of the dark！？
O-Ouch... Hah！
Ah, I fell asleep？ Whoa, what a surprise...
But that nurse Nightingale... I mean, you were so cute... Teehee, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
(It seems I would sneeze soon...)
(I have to light the candle...)

Manaka
Hmm, I have to go to prep school today, and piano class tomorrow, and ballet class the day after, and...
(Huh？ I think I've seen this girl from somewhere before... She looks so lonely. What's wrong？)
What is it, big brother？ You're staring at Manaka.
One moment... So you are Manaka-chan？
Yes, Takane Manaka, grade 2.
(▲高嶺＊＊▲！？ I-I guess so... But why is she like that？)
...What's wrong with my bag？
That's my flute. I have a test tomorrow.
I got my gym shirt and shorts in there... Eh？ What's the matter？
Kyaa！ That's the crime alert buzzer！
Hey！ Don't just go touching things as you please！
Sorry...
Manaka is too busy. No time to play with you, big brother.
Does Manaka-chan always go home alone like this？ Where are your friends？
Everyone else is still at school, playing...
Then why didn't Manaka-chan stay and play at school too？
Manaka has to go to prep school today, and a piano lesson tomorrow... So Manaka has to go home before everyone else.
(I see. She told me once before that she attended a lot of classes...)
(She said she chose to do them... But she must feel lonely because she can't play with her friends...)
And what are you doing here, big brother？
Eh？ That's because I saw Manaka-chan's sad face...
I'm not sad. If I do my best in my classes, Papa and Mama will praise me. I'll be happy.
Is that really how you feel？
Manaka-chan？
A... Actually... I'm... I'm.... really sad...！ ...Yeah...
But...
If I say that... Papa and Mama will...
There, there. It's okay. Manaka-chan, do you want to play with this big brother today then？
Eh？ But my prep school... I'll be scolded...
It's okay. This big brother will apologize to the school for you.
R... Really？
Really. Let's do something fun. So, stop crying now.
Big brother...！
警官
You...！
Huh？ Police？
I heard the crime alert buzzer... What are you doing here？
Um, that was just a false alarm. Right, Manaka-chan？
Yes... This big brother wanted Manaka to skip prep school. He said he'd do something fun with Manaka！
...Can you go with me to the police station？
Your explanation was so bad, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！ It's a misunderstanding！
I was thinking that you were cute, but...
...Eh？ Ah！ ...A dream？
(What on the school bag？)

Please don't make me a loser with the bad ending！

But I feel like I've seen something I wasn't supposed to see...
Somehow, my heart is throbbing...

...Where is this place？ It's all dark...
Manaka
Shhh！ Romeo, lower your voice or we will be found out.
That voice... ▲高嶺＊＊▲！？ Wait a minute. That costume...
This dress？ I didn't want to be conspicuous, so I picked this plain outfit. Does it suit me？
It doesn't look bad, but... What's with this Romeo thing？
Well, you are Romeo. O Romeo, Romeo！ Wherefore art thou Romeo？
I am Romeo...？
My Romeo... Deny thy father and refuse thy name.
Um... That means... You are Juliet？
Did you forget, my beloved Romeo...？
Our love won't lose to anyone. Ah, I can feel your presence so close like this...
Hey, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. Are we in a stage play or something？
Yes, we have to act as if we don't know each other in front of everyone... The whole world is our stage！
Please, Romeo. Take me away from here！ We will find a place to live, where no one can find us...
I can't do that！ Your family will be worried sick.
I don't care. You are much more important to me than my family. So...
(Her acting is so real. You make my heart throb ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Please. Take my hand, and free me from this confined cage！
O-Okay！ I got it！
Then reach out for me... I am right here.
(Urgh... She's on the second floor. How can I reach her...？)
Romeo！ Reach me！
Ah... Romeo. Now, I have become free, right...？
衛兵
You！ What are you doing！
Ah！ The patrolman... Run, Romeo！
What about you, Juliet！？
You mustn't worry about me. Please flee for now！
But I can't leave you alone... I shall have a sword duel with him...
Romeo, you would risk yourself for me...
If I can't be with you, there's no reason for me to be alive...
I don't mind putting my life at risk, as long as I can stay with you！
...Romeo！
Hey！ You are a Montague...！
I feel sorry for you, but for me and my Juliet, I can't allow anyone to get in my way！
Bring it on！
Romeoooooooo！！
Julieeeeeeet！ ...Eh？ A dream...？ Hah...
Anyway, looked good in Juliet's costume... ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
(I have to hold Juliet's hand...)

Where am I？ This place is full of spectators...
Manaka
This is our final match. Don't keep looking around！
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Don't just say "Ah"！ Get serious！
If we don't cooperate with each other, we can't win this match.
Well, you keep saying "final match" and such... What's going on？
It's the tournament, of course. Once we win this match, our mixed doubles team will become the world champion.
T-The world champion！？
実況
Now the tennis tournament to determine the world championship has begun！ Takane is here to take the challenge！
Yah！
Takane, nice serve！ As expected from the angel of the tennis court, MANAKA▼TAKANE is perfect as always！
It's coming to you now！
Whoa, it really came this way！ ...Hiya！
What's wrong？ Concentrate！
Yes, just like that！
(Thank goodness. Somehow, I managed to return the ball...)
I'm not going to lose！ ...Yah！
There it is！ Takane's jump smash, "Air MANA"！
Air MANA！？ She even has her own special technique！？
Now, stay focused and let's go！
As expected from my angel！ She's close to becoming the world champion！
(She is not yours！！)
I think the other team is getting more serious... Here it comes！
Oh no！ The ball was hit back to Takane's partner！ This is bad. That partner is unacceptably unreliable！
Stop saying whatever you want. ...Yah！
Nice return！ I'll reward you for this later！
What reward！？ I hate this partner！ Now, let's ignore her partner, who happened to return the ball nicely, and just cheer for Takane！
(What's with this announcer...？)
What's the matter？ Concentrate！ Here comes their miracle ball！
M-Miracle ball！？
Right. When you hit it, you might be blown out of the stadium. It's their special technique！
This miracle ball won't hurt any female, so you can rest assured. But it can cause serious injury to male players.
Wait, wait, this miracle ball can hurt me then！
Watch out！ Hit the ball！
What！？ Whoa... The ball is so heavy...！
It's a contest of strength with their miracle ball！ Do your best and hit it！
But this ball is... No, I can't hit it... Whoooaaa！
Awwwwwww！ Takane's partner couldn't return the ball and was blown away！
Ah, hey！ Before you're blown away, say your catch phrase！ Hurry！
I-I'll remember this！！
W-What？ That was a dream？ Hah... What a dream...
But, ▲高嶺＊＊▲ was really cool...
(I have to receive that ball！)

Whoa, it's getting deep into fall, the beautiful season of leaves changing colors...
Manaka
Here, a roasted sweet potato.
▲高嶺＊＊▲... Thanks.
Hehe, when you think of fall, you think of roasted potatoes, right？ They're full of fiber, so they're good for your health.
Girls love roasted potatoes, I guess. But I like them, too.
They're delicious, of course, and they make you enjoy the season to its fullness.
Indeed, it's the wonderful feeling of fall.
Yup. Hehe, this potato is so good！
You really like roasted potatoes, huh？
Because of that, I tend to overeat. After this, I'll have to exercise.
Fall is best for foods as well as sports. It's such a healthy season.
Yeah. Since I'm going to exercise, should I eat another one？
Yeah, go for it. You'd better eat more. It's fun to watch you eat, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Haha！ Well then...
I'll pretend I didn't hear it.
What's that sound？
(That sound just now...)
A-All right. I guess I'll eat one more, too！ Roasted potatoes are so good, haha！
...What？ If there's something you want to say, just say it.
Eh？ Umm... That's....
Ah！ I think I might have just farted！ Sorry, hahaha！
...Wouldn't you yourself know whether you did or didn't？
Well, these roasted potatoes are so delicious, I didn't notice myself fart！ No, really！
(Urgh, I should've known that it was too forced...)
...Thanks.
Hm？
Well！ Yes, please help yourself to another roasted potato.
Uh, that sound just now was...
Hey, just now, you made that sound, didn't you？
D-Did it seem like it...？
Yeah, it was definitely you. A poooo~ sound.
W-Wasn't it the sound of the bench creaking？
No, it wasn't. It sounded like the voice of an insect or the cry of a small animal. It was a cute sound.
T-That's...
What did you say？
Are you possibly teasing me...？
What are you talking about？ Besides, I'm still worried about the sound...
...Idiot. Stupid. I hate you！
Eh！？ Why are you so angry？
Hah！ It's a dream...
You being embarrassed is really cute ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Somehow, I want to see you like that again ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Manaka
It's starting soon, isn't it？ I'm excited.
...Huh？ This is...？ What's going to start, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Sumo... I was pushy with my invitation before. Was it a bother？
Well, you said earlier that you wanted to watch sumo...
By the way, do you like sumo wrestling？
Not much.
Really, young people these days don't watch sumo... I guess it can't be helped...
("Young people"？ You're not that old yourself ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Ah, look, there's the wrestler I'm cheering for. It's good that we got such good seats...
Now that you mentioned it, aren't these premium box seats？ Weren't they expensive？
As long as we could watch this match, I thought I'd splurge. Hey, look at his well-trained body！
Well, I don't want to be rude, but I can't really tell whether he's well-trained or not...
Yeah, you probably can't tell... But, inside that body is a mass of muscles.
For such a body to perform the first quick charge, physical strength is a must！
Really？ Have you always been this into sumo, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
To be honest, that's right... I love sumo more than three meals a day！ It's irresistible！
(More than food！？ You're getting too excited ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Ah, looks like it's about to begin. Kyaa~！ Go for it！
(Her eyes are sparkling. I've never seen her in such high spirits until now...)
Amazing force in that clash right after the first charge！ Hey, are you listening？
Y-Yeah. It looked more powerful in person than on TV.
Go~~！
(▲高嶺＊＊▲... She's voicing her support！？)
Yes, he won！ Wonderful！！
Hehe, of course, sumo wrestlers look wonderful...
...Say, is someone like these sumo wrestlers your type, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Hmm, I wonder. I've never thought about it seriously before... Why？
I think I might get a bit jealous somehow...
Oh, really... Will you try to become a sumo wrestler, then？
Eh？
I'll make you lots of food every day！ Are you going to practice and build up your body？
I-I can't eat anymore~！ ...Huh？ A dream...？
Somehow, I feel like I just blurted out some incredibly cliched lines. What a valuable experience.
